"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-australia-news-sport-two-injured-stars-named-in-matildas-squad-for-paris-olympics-as-coach-tony-gustavsson-makes-shock-omission-news-story-e06975164c1a5b030345eb703db3b316\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Matildas' 18-player squad for the Paris Olympics has been unveiled, with coach Tony Gustavsson hoping a couple of shock decisions will pay off.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 52, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 98, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Gustavsson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Gustavsson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Gustavsson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Gustavsson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Matildas coach Tony Gustavsson has taken a gamble on his Olympics squad, with one promising star missing out while two players carrying injuries make the cut.\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 149, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7828467402723044e-89, \"text\": \"Matildas\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Gustavsson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Gustavsson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Gustavsson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Gustavsson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 18-player squad was named on Tuesday morning, more than 12 hours after Australia were farewelled by a rampant home crowd in their last home game before their campaign in Paris.\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 384, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.974172976243666e-66, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.252110387795968e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vital forward Caitlin Foord has been selected despite carrying a hamstring injury while midfielder Kaitlin Gorry was also picked while dealing with an ankle issue that kept her out of Monday's match.\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Foord\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Foord\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Foord\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Foord\"}, {\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaitlin_Doubleday\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaitlin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaitlin_Doubleday\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaitlin_Doubleday\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both players have just under two months to get back to full fitness before their first match against Germany on July 25 (local time).\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 793, \"end\": 800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999984537769836, \"rank\": 1.5462252873031044e-06, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Young defender and fan favourite Charlotte Grant was left out of the squad in heartbreaking news for the 22-year-old who has been a mainstay of the senior squad in the last three years and was a part of the Matildas' team at the Tokyo Olympics in 2021.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Grant\", \"score\": 0.9999794718061584, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Grant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Veteran goalkeeper Lydia Williams, who is retiring from international football after the Olympics, was also not picked however she has been named as a travelling reserve player along with Grant, Sharn Freier and Courtney Nevin.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lydia_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lydia Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lydia_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lydia_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 1293, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtney_Nevin\", \"score\": 0.9999993772059618, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Courtney Nevin\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtney_Nevin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtney_Nevin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reserves can be selected as a replacement in the team in case of an injury or withdrawal from one of the 18 players named.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Captain Sam Kerr is the biggest name missing from the squad, after she was officially ruled out last month with the striker continuing her recovery from an anterior cruciate ligament (ACL) injury she suffered in January while in a mid-season training camp in Morocco with club side Chelsea FC.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kerr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Kerr\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kerr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kerr\"}, {\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament_injury\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"anterior cruciate ligament (ACL) injury\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament_injury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament_injury\"}, {\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999490683, \"rank\": 5.091569541754329e-10, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\"