"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a 1-1 draw in Adelaide on Friday, the match in Sydney was heading for a similar result with scores locked at half-time.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2279, \"end\": 2285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Swans\", \"score\": 0.9993474208096765, \"rank\": 0.0005137442999640523, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Swans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Swans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Substitute Clare Wheeler stepped up when she broke the deadlock with a header from a Catley free kick early in the second stanza.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Wheeler\", \"score\": 0.9999922392813563, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clare Wheeler\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Wheeler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Wheeler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hayley Raso sealed the result with a tidy finish after she was put through on goal by an incisive Cortnee Vine pass.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hayley_Raso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hayley Raso\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hayley_Raso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hayley_Raso\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia plays Germany on July 25 local time (July 26 3am AEST), Zambia on July 28 local time (July 29 3am AEST) and the United States on July 31 local time (August 1 3am AEST).\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2602, \"end\": 2611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.974172976243666e-66, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999984537769836, \"rank\": 1.5462252873031044e-06, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2710, \"end\": 2714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Full squad: Mackenzie Arnold, Ellie Carpenter, Steph Catley, Kyra Cooney-Cross, Caitlin Foord, Mary Fowler, Katrina Gorry, Michelle Heyman, Clare Hunt, Alanna Kennedy, Teagan Micah, Clare Polkinghorne, Hayley Raso, Kaitlyn Torpey, Emily Van Egmond, Cortnee Vine, Clare Wheeler, Tameka Yallop.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 3074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2812, \"end\": 2827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Carpenter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellie Carpenter\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Carpenter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Carpenter\"}, {\"begin\": 2829, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steph_Catley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steph Catley\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"